Project Setup Notes
- Create a new project: `django-admin startproject onlineStore`
- Create apps:
  - `python manage.py startapp products`
  - `python manage.py startapp aboutus`
  - `python manage.py startapp contactus`
- Add the three apps to `INSTALLED_APPS`.
- Create templates using template inheritance (base + child pages).
- Run the server: `python manage.py runserver`

